title: Number 10 Pizza
synopsis: At the end of activities you do with your child today, have a number 10 countdown! Just before it's time to clean up or transition, count together from 10 to 1. Then you're done!

title: Happy Thoughts Song

title: The First Monster President

title: How You Play the Game
synopsis: Play a fun game with your child like red light, green light. Afterward, talk about how playing fair and trying your best are more important than winning or losing.

title: Happy Tapping with Elmo

title: Seven Fish with Elmo

title: Romeo Santos: Quiero Ser Tu Amigo
